        <p>Meeting minimum requirements means the game will run, but you'll likely need to play on low settings at 30 FPS or below. You may experience stuttering, long loading times, and reduced visual quality. For a comfortable experience at 60 FPS with decent settings, aim for recommended specs or better.</p>
      </div>
