      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>System requirements are based on official publisher specifications and community testing. They typically target 30 FPS at minimum specs and 60 FPS at recommended specs, usually at 1080p resolution. Actual performance may vary based on drivers, background processes, and specific game scenes. Always check recent benchmarks for your specific hardware combination.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
